stlmaps

Angela Kothe

4/26/2021

I had an assignment to make a map of a city and add a feature to it from Open Street Maps. I added three, to tell a story about my summer of 2020.

In Summer 2020, I moved back to St.Louis City.

St.Louis is a beer town, and has a lot of bars.

And it has some breweries too.

In summer 2020, I was a resident of three different neighborhoods in St.Louis. For a month, I lived on top of a bar called the Ninth Street Deli in Soulard. It was right next to Anheuser-Bush.
